---
title: Apricot-Glazed Falafel Nourish Plate with Roasted Veggies, Slaw, Pine Nuts & Garlic Dip
description: Make friends with plant-based ingredients by teaming hearty falafels with some stellar sides: chermoula
roasted veggies, a crunchy salad, and a garlic dip so flavourful, you'll want to add it to everything.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
